    <item>
      <title>中国越来越将特朗普领导下的美国视为一个衰落的帝国</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/12/business/china-trump-xi-decline.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几十年来，许多中国人对美国的看法夹杂着钦佩、嫉妒和怨恨。特朗普总统不稳定的第二任期打破了这一形象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/12/business/china-trump-xi-decline.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 04:00:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
