    <item>
      <title>投票权决定可能会让田纳西州费耶特县的黑人保持沉默</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/11/us/fayette-county-tennessee-voting-rights.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[占田纳西州费耶特县 25% 的黑人居民去年赢得了新的选举地图，更换了全白人委员会。他们担心最高法院的裁决可能会威胁到这一点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/11/us/fayette-county-tennessee-voting-rights.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 19:49:37 GMT</pubDate>
